# Copy to .env ONLY if you can't use 1Password CLI or macOS Keychain.
# .env is gitignored. Never commit the real key. Never paste it into chat.
# Preference order: 1Password CLI > Keychain > env > .env (see SECURITY.md).

# Last-resort key storage (plaintext on disk — avoid if you can):
# GRANOLA_API_KEY=

# 1Password secret reference this tool reads by default (no key on disk at all):
# GRANOLA_OP_REF=op://Private/Granola/credential

# Optional overrides (defaults shown):
# GRANOLA_API_BASE=https://public-api.granola.ai/v1
# GRANOLA_KEYCHAIN_SERVICE=granola-api-key
